      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;plan&#34;&gt;Plan&lt;a href=&#34;#plan&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;plan is extremally simple:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Install Debian on server.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Install the media Drive.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Install Nextcloud and monitoring/displaying software to make it all pretty.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;debian-install&#34;&gt;Debian Install&lt;a href=&#34;#debian-install&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This step i thought would take somewhere around a hour but i was stuck here for &lt;strong&gt;3 days&lt;/strong&gt;. the thing was that i didn&amp;rsquo;t had beefy enough USB drive, but as always i would realize that far into the project, after i would try every possible configuration starting from Rufus all the way to the custom made ISOs, but nothing worked other than &lt;strong&gt;most bizarre solution&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
